{"snp4.2:0.1":"Sutta Nipata 4.2 ","snp4.2:0.2":"Guhatthakasutta ","snp4.2:1.1":"Satto guhayam bahunabhichanno, ","snp4.2:1.2":"Tittham naro mohanasmim pagalho; ","snp4.2:1.3":"Dure viveka hi tathavidho so, ","snp4.2:1.4":"Kama hi loke na hi suppahaya. ","snp4.2:2.1":"Icchanidana bhavasatabaddha, ","snp4.2:2.2":"Te duppamunca na hi annamokkha; ","snp4.2:2.3":"Paccha pure vapi apekkhamana, ","snp4.2:2.4":"Ime va kame purime va jappam. ","snp4.2:3.1":"Kamesu giddha pasuta pamulha, ","snp4.2:3.2":"Avadaniya te visame nivittha; ","snp4.2:3.3":"Dukkhupanita paridevayanti, ","snp4.2:3.4":"Kimsu bhavissama ito cutase. ","snp4.2:4.1":"Tasma hi sikkhetha idheva jantu, ","snp4.2:4.2":"Yam kinci janna visamanti loke; ","snp4.2:4.3":"Na tassa hetu visamam careyya, ","snp4.2:4.4":"Appanhidam jivitamahu dhira. ","snp4.2:5.1":"Passami loke pariphandamanam, ","snp4.2:5.2":"Pajam imam tanhagatam bhavesu; ","snp4.2:5.3":"Hina nara maccumukhe lapanti, ","snp4.2:5.4":"Avitatanhase bhavabhavesu. ","snp4.2:6.1":"Mamayite passatha phandamane, ","snp4.2:6.2":"Maccheva appodake khinasote; ","snp4.2:6.3":"Etampi disva amamo careyya, ","snp4.2:6.4":"Bhavesu asattimakubbamano. ","snp4.2:7.1":"Ubhosu antesu vineyya chandam, ","snp4.2:7.2":"Phassam parinnaya ananugiddho; ","snp4.2:7.3":"Yadattagarahi tadakubbamano, ","snp4.2:7.4":"Na lippati ditthasutesu dhiro. ","snp4.2:8.1":"Sannam parinna vitareyya ogham, ","snp4.2:8.2":"Pariggahesu muni nopalitto; ","snp4.2:8.3":"Abbulhasallo caramappamatto, ","snp4.2:8.4":"Nasisati lokamimam parancati. ","snp4.2:8.5":"Guhatthakasuttam dutiyam. "}